- ctrl + 1 > assign statement to new local variable  ---> Set new local variable

- Type 'main' > ctrl + Space > Enter ---> Gives 'pubic static void main(String[] args)' automatically.  

- Type 'syso' > ctrl + Space > enter ---> Gives 'System.out.println()' automatically.  
 
- ctrl + 1 > select your choice ---> Fix any error automatically in eclipse.  

- ctrl + shift + f ---> Format document. 

- ctrl + d ---> Delete line. 

- ctrl + alt + up/down arrow-key ---> Duplicate line. 



